{"word":"H3245 - יָסַד - yâçad - yaw-sad' - Appoint","slug":"H3245","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָסַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâçad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-sad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appoint"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E1;&#x05D3; - ya&#x0302;sad</b> - <i>yaw-sad'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>set</i> (literally or figuratively); intensively to <i>found</i>; reflexively to <i>sit</i> down together, that is, <i>settle</i>, <i>consult: - </i>appoint, take counsel, establish, (lay the, lay for a) found (-ation), instruct, lay, ordain, set, X sure."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3246\">H3246</a>, <a href=\"#/H3247\">H3247</a>, <a href=\"#/H3248\">H3248</a>, <a href=\"#/H4143\">H4143</a>, <a href=\"#/H4144\">H4144</a>, <a href=\"#/H4145\">H4145</a>, <a href=\"#/H4146\">H4146</a>, <a href=\"#/H4328\">H4328</a>, <a href=\"#/H4527\">H4527</a>"}]}